snippet.title: Whiteout - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Whiteout is finally here and fully released. Complete with an entire new map, entire new story, new cutscenes and animations, new music, new voice acting, and much more.
Trailer 3/3.

You play as a secret service agent.
 Your agency has sent you out to frigid Northern Canada to investigate a private company known as Crescent Inc... 
The company is off the grid and nested deep in the mountains.
You are on a cargo transfer flight with 2 other passengers, no commercial flights go this far up north.

Download Link: https://kaiclark.itch.io/whiteout-redux
